Need proven software development firm experienced with commercializing SaaS
text:
We have a software development start-up who has outgrown our capabilities. We will introduce them to a proven software development firm who is experienced with commercializing SaaS applications.

Requirements: - Team is Based in US - Waterfall / Agile Development - Scalable Architecture - Must speak English clearly - They will start working with new team in early 2023 - Ready to meet with Founder ASAP - Work / Meet California Time - Work with successful / perfectionist / demanding Founder - Multi-Tenant Software - Has expert Product Manager - Has expert QA Team - Gather requirements from Founder and team

We developed their internal version on this development stack:

ASP.NET Core (App Service on Azure) C# (C-sharp) Angular SQL Server (Azure) MediaWiki for Help docs (Virtual Machine on Azure) GitHub (Source code)

Please send intro / mobile to discuss this further.
